name: "Full Moon Night"
description:
A"Full moon night" is part of the "Simultaneous Definitive Routine" collection.
Smoking weed with your friends, relaxed. 
What are you talking about? Surely Art, sure Design.
What is your favorite avant-garde? The only manifesto that interests them is the one where we are protagonists.
They sure talk about how well they are going to have a good weekend when the whole group gets together.

Thank`s for the support! It`s a great help for my work to continue improving!
